2016 Demographics for Software Carpentry Learners

Revised: 2018-02-28
Lead: Kari L. Jordan, Director of Assessment and Community Equity

The following includes demographic data for those individuals who took Software Carpentry’s pre-workshop survey in 2016. There were a total 5896 learners who completed this survey in 2016.
